_sText:
I just detailed it, removed almost all secrets, added some new. I also added playground (carousel, sandbox, swings, slide), football (ball will automatically teleport in center) and basketball, balcony and two health-chargers from Half-Life 2.

### Armory:

- 4 x AWP
- 10 x AK47
- 10 x M4A1
- 6 x MP5
- 3 x M3
- 8 x smokegrenades
- 15 x flashbangs
- 3 x deagle dispensers (24 deagles max from all dispensers)
- 2 x nade dispensers (24 nades max from all dispensers)

### Other changes:

They're 16 random secrets in jails. Every round 1 glock spawns in random jail.


### Slots:
18xCT
16xT
